  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Drug-Free Pain Management Awareness Month</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Our nationwide campaign is crucial in raising public awareness of the dangers of abusing prescription drugs for pain management &amp; that chiropractic care is the preferred first-line drug-free approach to safely &amp; effectively manage low back, neck &amp; neuro-musculoskeletal pain. Opioid &amp; drug overdose deaths are continuing to increase in the U.S. with 65,000 opioid deaths 2016. 80% of drug abusers begin the downward spiral with prescription painkillers, which are given by doctors who overprescribe.</narrative>
  </description>
